---
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About"
	description="About AI Tools Hub"
	pubDate={new Date('November 11 2025')}
>
	<div class="about-content">
		<h2>About AI Tools Hub</h2>
		
		<p>
			We're a team of developers and content creators who got tired of wasting hours 
			comparing AI tools. So we built this site to save you time.
		</p>

		<h3>What We Do</h3>
		<p>
			We test AI tools, compare features, and publish honest reviews. No marketing fluff. 
			Just real data from real testing.
		</p>

		<h3>Why Trust Us?</h3>
		<ul>
			<li>Every tool is tested hands-on</li>
			<li>We include both pros and cons</li>
			<li>We update reviews as tools evolve</li>
			<li>We disclose all affiliate relationships</li>
		</ul>

		<h3>Who We Help</h3>
		<p>
			Content creators, developers, marketers, and anyone looking to leverage AI 
			without wasting money on the wrong tools.
		</p>

		<h3>Contact</h3>
		<p>
			Questions or suggestions? Email us at: 
			<a href="mailto:contact@ai-tools-hub.com">contact@ai-tools-hub.com</a>
		</p>
	</div>

	<style>
		.about-content h3 {
			margin-top: 2rem;
		}

		.about-content ul {
			list-style-position: inside;
		}

		.about-content li {
			margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
		}
	</style>
</Layout>
